
# StudyBuddy 📚🤖  
**Your AI-Powered Study Companion for Smarter Learning**

---

## Overview 🎯  
**StudyBuddy** is an innovative, AI-driven study assistant designed to streamline the learning process for students and professionals. From capturing lecture audio to organizing detailed notes with equations and diagrams, StudyBuddy is your all-in-one academic ally.

---

## Features ✨  

### 🔊 Real-Time Transcription  
- Accurately transcribe lecture audio in real-time.  

### 🖼️ Visual Content Recognition  
- Convert lecture slides and diagrams into text and searchable notes.

### 🧮 Equation Magic  
- Render complex equations into LaTeX for clear and organized representation.

### 📋 Summarization & Organization  
- Generate concise summaries and structured outlines automatically.

### 🗂️ Smart Note Organization  
- Tag, highlight, and categorize notes for easy access.

### 🌐 Multi-Language Support  
- Transcribe and process content in multiple languages.

### 📄 Flexible Exports  
- Export notes to Markdown or PDF for offline access and sharing.

---

## Tech Stack ⚙️  
- **React.js**: Dynamic user interface.  
- **Tailwind CSS**: Sleek, responsive design.  
- **React Speech Recognition**: Real-time transcription.  
- **Tesseract.js & Simpletex API**: Convert images to text and LaTeX.  
- **Mermaid.js**: Generate diagrams and flowcharts.  
- **Google Gemini LLM**: Integrate audio and visual data for cohesive notes.  
- **Firebase**: Secure, cloud-based note storage.

---

